---
title: Zesty Roasted Dukkah Potatoes with Feta & Dill | Serves 2
description: You can never, ever go wrong with crispy roasted potatoes. But we've added aromatic dill and salty, creamy feta to make a side dish that's a little bit fancy and absolutely irresistible.
